Introduction

Lubless (Korean: 러블레스; Japanese: ラブレス) is a South Korean band under Alive Now consisting of two members: Lena and Bongwoo. They debuted on January 2, 2020 with the single album Bluebird (파랑새). The band’s name stands for “Lust Bless You”.
